{"tid":2210056,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"現金奇缺 業界求「財」若渴","createTime":"2020-09-20T06:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T07:09:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d78b1f2df2207455fbe35ddee3eb522167a0ec5","tid":2210056,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/57K4FCCIVFE75DHXTPJZIOJE64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2F57K4FCCIVFE75DHXTPJZIOJE64%2F&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmsQbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=e4c97438\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2F57K4FCCIVFE75DHXTPJZIOJE64%2F&h=2c4d2ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/57K4FCCIVFE75DHXTPJZIOJE64/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n現金奇缺 業界求「財」若渴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XFFFGiGiEJFReXjWCrny2vC34v8=/3022x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DO62DMM7FRA5DMXFIGC2FL5FXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXFFFGiGiEJFReXjWCrny2vC34v8%3D%2F3022x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDO62DMM7FRA5DMXFIGC2FL5FXY.jpg&h=dfc10208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■澳門8月博彩收入按年大跌94.5%，業界期望恢復自由行可拯救生意。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】澳門經濟兩支柱觀光業和博彩業受到疫情嚴重打擊，遊客進不去，賭場生意暴跌九成以上，賭業面對寒冬。<br />\n<br />\n不少澳門賭廳出現缺港元現金情況，有賭客甚至無法兌換籌碼。。。。。。。。。。，紛紛撲現金應付賭客，「啲客係咁攞錢，好似銀行擠提」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利息高 富豪多存款賭廳<br />\n<br />\n澳門賭業知情人士向《蘋果》爆料表示，自武漢肺炎疫情後賭廳紛紛出現缺現金情況，。。。。。。。。。。。。加上賭廳剛開返冇耐好靜，得小貓三、四隻，現金流少咗好多」。<br />\n<br />\n內地打擊洗黑錢亦影響賭廳現金額，。。。。。。。。。。。。，而且內地政府都𥄫實呢啲地下錢莊，賭廳要轉錢變得難上加難」。<br />\n<br />\n賭廳的港元現金少，卻遇上「擠提」。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「賭廳好似銀行擠提咁，完全唔夠錢畀人攞，惟有向地下錢莊買現金，當然亦係要抽水，買100萬現金可能只攞到八、九成」。<br />\n<br />\n澳門賭廳缺現金又缺客，有叠馬仔為了交數，維持一定的兌換籌碼數額，「佢哋會以八折或八五折出售籌碼搶客，如果交唔夠數，佢哋會俾賭廳老闆踢走」。<br />\n<br />\n澳門繼早前恢復珠海及廣東旅客自由行簽註，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「估計十一黃金周將至，將迎來數以萬計遊客，帶旺返整個澳門，現金流又會多返，應該可以捱過去」。<br />\n<br />\n澳門博彩監察協調局本月初公佈，。。。。。。。。。。。，並連續五個月按年跌幅逾九成。"},{"pid":"c1f4e00a040e897c7e33473c60af06dfce54052b","tid":2210056,"uid":17857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"吸毒經濟，淨係諗住點樣吊癮，唔諗點樣轉型，自己攞嚟"},{"pid":"870483103494ddbb80b0c110cbc964b830d0684e","tid":2210056,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"唔明，支屬澳門唔係用人民幣咩？"},{"pid":"2449c09d8aa18bfdec7b6946517e6322e1cad09e","tid":2210056,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"廢藍：你睇吓澳門聽聽話話過得幾好，人均gdp世界第一。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2cbffd96c5fc5abd4e43ad123cf44cdfa72f67","tid":2210056,"uid":134227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />澳門唔係立左23條就會經濟好咩"},{"pid":"5afb57e064c9fd66551c9abc5a7da97720bd6f5d","tid":2210056,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"完全唔明澳門同中国零確診咁耐<br />\n<br />\n又有健康碼<br />\n<br />\n唔係一早通左關？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cea1a8f3680164b1deb1db111fb5268a34ee85","tid":2210056,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"有咁耐風流"},{"pid":"e777351aa2f0aa543f81cf4cbd9120c26782c683","tid":2210056,"uid":210922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5afb57e064c9fd66551c9abc5a7da97720bd6f5d","tid":2210056,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"完全唔明澳門同中国零確診咁耐<br />\n<br />\n又有健康碼<br />\n<br />\n唔係一早通左關？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"通關係商務證，外勞同有港